nroffed_file ({0,2,4,"soul","Discworld player help","soul","Name",7,5,"soul - the wonderful feelings thing.","Pinkfish's soul.How to use (What can it do for you?):",3,5,5,"        The feeling or atmosphere commands that you use, like smile and so on come from your soul.  The soul used on this mud is different to most others you will have come across.  Below are a few examples of what you can do with this soul. ",7,5,"> smile happilly at furballYou smile happily at furball.> smile w at furballYou smile wryly at furball> shake hands with furballYou shake hands with furball> shake hands furballYou shake hands with furball.",3,5,5,"The above are a few examples of what can be done with the soul.  The usage of the command (ie whether you use and at or a with or whatever... well, just use what seems right... It should work)  To see what soul commands are available to you at any given time type ",7,5,"> look at soulHere are the commands in this hooppy soul.#smile*       cry        poke+",3,5,5,"Ok interpretation of the listing... (first degree course).  The # at the front of the name, as in #smile, means that there are substitutable paramaters. This mean that things are possible using this soul command.  To find all the possible paramaters for a given soul comand use it and put in something that is definately invalid. ie ",7,5,"> shake jshdfWrong... Error message:  head,leg,arm",3,5,5,"The first one of the options is the default.  You can select the others by doing things like ",7,5,"> shake lYou shake your leg.> shake armYou shake your arm.",3,5,5,"Any of the soul commands displayed in the long list have help available for them.  This help shows you all the valid methods of using the soul command and all the valid adverbs to the commands.Womble on. If you find a missing command use the following command to get it added by someone who can.soul <text> ","Examples",7,5,"soul bleed - I want to be able to bleed on people.soul kick - I keep typing kick pinkfish and it fails!soul snickersoul smile spasmodically would be cute","See also",7,5,"alias, history, help",})
